history.prompt:
Fix the clicker game: Create a RemoteEvent named 'ClickEvent' in ReplicatedStorage. Add a Leaderstats script to ServerScriptService that gives +1 Click when 'ClickEvent' is fired. Update the GUI button to fire this 'ClickEvent'."

Vagy, ha biztosra akarsz menni, itt a kód, amit a szerverednek most ki kellene köpnie. Figyeld a logot, ha ezt látod, akkor működni fog:

[
  {
    "action": "executeLua",
    "code": "local rs = game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'); if not rs:FindFirstChild('ClickEvent') then Instance.new('RemoteEvent', rs).Name = 'ClickEvent' end"
  },
  {
    "action": "createScript",
    "name": "LeaderstatsFix",
    "scriptType": "Script",
    "parent": "ServerScriptService",
    "content": "game.Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(player) local ls = Instance.new('Folder', player); ls.Name = 'leaderstats'; local clicks = Instance.new('IntValue', ls); clicks.Name = 'Clicks'; clicks.Value = 0 end); game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):WaitForChild('ClickEvent').OnServerEvent:Connect(function(player) player.leaderstats.Clicks.Value += 1 end)"
  },
  {
    "action": "executeLua",
    "code": "local player = game.Players.LocalPlayer; local gui = player:WaitForChild('PlayerGui'):FindFirstChild('ClickerGui', true); if gui then local btn = gui:FindFirstChildOfClass('TextButton', true); if btn then btn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').ClickEvent:FireServer() end) end end"
  }
